prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon slice of cherry pie with big, googly eyes and a wide, mischievous grin, wearing a tiny birthday party hat at a jaunty angle. It's energetically running away, leaving a trail of fruity filling splatters behind it. Floating above the pie, in the safe center area, is the text "Hope your birthday is as sweet as stolen pie" in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is a flat 2D artwork in a vibrant watercolor painting style, with soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges.
